    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Clean, good-condition vehicle that runs and drives well and should make a solid daily driver. It presents nicely overall with normal wear for its age and use, including some minor cosmetic blemishes and light signs of use inside and out, but nothing out of line for a well-kept used car. Interior is in good shape, exterior shows well, and everything gives the impression of a vehicle that has been cared for even if it is not mint. Buyers can expect an honest, dependable used vehicle with typical cosmetic imperfections rather than a showroom example.",
