    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Absolutely stunning in every respect, this mint-condition vehicle has been exceptionally well cared for and presents beautifully inside and out. It offers a refined drive, a spotless cabin, and the kind of fit, finish, and overall condition discerning buyers look for. A rare opportunity to own a truly premium used vehicle that stands out for its quality, pride of ownership, and long-term value.",
