    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Mint-condition example that\u2019s been clearly cared for and presents exactly the way you want a premium used car to present\u2014clean body, sharp paint, tidy interior, and a drivetrain that feels strong, smooth, and properly sorted. It starts easily, idles cleanly, shifts as it should, and tracks confidently down the road with composed steering, solid braking, and no excuses. All the right signs of attentive ownership are here, from the well-kept cabin to the overall fit, finish, and mechanical feel. If you\u2019ve been waiting for one that stands out from the usual worn, neglected listings, this is the one to see.",
      "price": 46900.0,
